laboratory_examinations.findings: Biliary obstructive pattern - Tbil 2.1, Direct: 1.6, AST: 91, ALT: 47, Alphos: 196

Fluid density structure in hepatic segment V measuring up to 4.6 cm, moderate intrahepatic biliary ductal dilation, common bile duct dilation to 1.9 cm with choledocholithiasis, irregular and edematous gallbladder wall, and possible perforation.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: The fluid density structure was previously characterized as a cyst on MRI and is minimally changed.
